text: André Osterberger was a athlete from France. Osterberger competed at the 1952 Summer Olympics. He was born on 26 October 1920 and died on 18 January 2009.André Osterberger == References == Category:1920 births Category:2009 deaths Category:Hammer throwers Category:French athletes Category:Olympians for France Category:People from Côte-d'Or Category:Sportspeople from Bourgogne-Franche-Comté
